    <p><b><span class="arial221"><span style="color: #CC0000">
    <font face="Verdana">Remember!</font><font face="Verdana" size="2"> </font>
    </span><font face="Verdana" size="2"><font color="#000080">With Movers Arena you choose the estimates that you 
    need and you 
    always control your spending.</font></font></span><font face="Verdana" size="2"><font color="#000080"><br>
    </font>
    <br>
    <span class="arial221"><span style="color: #CC0000">Electronic Estimates</span></span><span style="color: #CC0000"><span class="arial221"><br>
    </span></span>All the estimates are stored in a secured personal database. 
    When you register with Movers Arena you will receive a username, password, and a 
    link to your private account. You will have access of 24/7 to your account. 
    The estimates are not being sent over the email. <br>
    <br>
    <span class="arial221">
    <span style="color: #CC0000">
    Sign me up!<br>
    </span>
    </span>We got you in our system, however we need to verify some information 
    before you make a <a href="http://www.moversarena.com/infosys/wc.dll?isutil~EMAILSREC~<%=ALLT(pcCUSTNO)%>~CCFORMS">deposit</a>.
    <span class="arial221"> <span style="color: #CC0000">
    <br>
    </span></span> <span style="color: #CC0000">
    <span class="arial221">
    <br>
    Sharing Estimates</span></span><br>
    The shared estimates can be sold up to five companies. <span class="arial221">
    <span style="color: #CC0000">Period! </span></span><br>
    <br>
    <span class="arial221"><span style="color: #CC0000">Exclusive Estimates</span></span><br>
    When an estimate has not been sold yet (&quot;taken&quot; is zero), the buyer has the option 
    to purchase this estimate exclusively. Meaning, the buyer is the only 
    company that will get this estimate. Usually exclusive estimates are being 
    sold three times higher than a single purchase. <br>
    <br>
    <span class="arial221"><span style="color: #CC0000">Favorites Service</span></span><br>
    Movers Arena sends you over the email the estimates that fit your needs. The 
    estimates are being sent immediately when they entered the system. This priority service gives you the 
    opportunity to be number-one buyer. You may alter your <a href="http://www.moversarena.com/wc.dll?mpreposit~arenain~XXX~<%=ALLT(pcCUSTNO)%>~RULESWC~?<%=SYS(2015)%>">favorites</a> any time.<br>
    <br>
    <span class="arial221"><span style="color: #CC0000">Affiliates</span></span><br>
    Movers Arena is affiliated with the following companies:<br>
    GRANOT, INC. - The Online Moving System<br>
    Relocations Network Media Group - Moving Directory<br>
    Moving411 - Moving Directory<br>
    5 Star Movers - Moving Directory<br>
    Moving Discount - Moving Directory</font></b></p>
    <p><b><font face="Verdana" size="2">
    <span class="arial221"><span style="color: #CC0000">Contact Us</span></span><br>
    <a href="mailto:estimates@moversarena.com">Contact us</a> For further 
    information.<br>
    &nbsp;</font></b></td>
